{
  "stem": "13673.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, to save postage, because neither of us had much money-- he maybe a few pennies more than I-- I would send him my letters.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he would add it to his own letters and send them on to Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But by the time the war began, this became increasingly difficult.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Red Cross allowed postcards to be sent with 25 words on them, I think in both directions.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm pretty sure but-- no, I think maybe just from Germany to England.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the 25 words, that would take about two months to reach England.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How they got it  there in the first place is a marvel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But 25 words-- all you can say and all anybody ever did say was, we're well, we'll see you soon.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Be good.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, only insofar as it changed everybody else's life in England.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were issued our gas masks, and we were issued our food rationing cards.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- we did drill-- air raid drills, and we had the black out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the war things that go on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I came back from this vacation and the war started is when Lonsdale House was no longer able to take boarders, and I guess they just took day students.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm-- I'm not sure if they did that right away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was even talk of closing the school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because Norwich is near the east coast, and the east coast is next-- is just across the water from Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- and there were-- there were bombing raids, and one thing and another.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then there was talk of inva-- fear of invasion, a  lot of rumors about that.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
